snippet.title: Corruption (1989) (Rainbird)
snippet.description:
Short play of Corruption, running on the Pi under ADFFS.  This is an APCS-A based game, that ADFFS gets running with a localized CLib 1

One of the Magnetic Scrolls adventures, which included Corruption, Fish!, The Guild of Thieves, Jinxter, The Pawn and Wonderland
